com.exlibris.dps.sdk.registry

Interface ConverterRegistryPlugin


  • public interface ConverterRegistryPlugin
    Interface for a ConverterRegistry plug-in type. The plugin converts a mets XMl to a different representation, in preparation for publishing. See PublisherRegistryPlugin for more information on the publishing process.
    This plugin interface only supports java implementation.
